#: pages/about.tsx:101
msgid "<strong>Universalis</strong> runs a REST API that applications can post market board data to, after they collect the data from a running game instance by multiple users, anonymously."
msgstr "<strong>Universalis</strong> 提供一個 REST API，應用程式可以匿名地從多位使用者正在執行的遊戲中收集市場交易板資料，之後將其上傳到該 API。"

