#: 
#~ msgctxt "alerts_whatisthis_guide_2"
#~ msgid "Alerts allow you to setup notification watchers that can track an item and send you information such as price changes or history events."
#~ msgstr "提醒功能讓您可以設定通知監控，追蹤特定物品並在價格變動或有歷史交易事件時通知您。"

#: 
#~ msgctxt "alerts_useraccount_guide_2"
#~ msgid "Alerts allow you to track all kinds of information about items on the market and be informed either by Discord or email for any changes that meet your requirements. To get started with creating alerts, go search for any item and then click on the Alert tab on the left."
#~ msgstr "提醒功能讓您可以追蹤市場上物品的各種資訊，並透過 Discord 或電子郵件通知任何符合您要求的變更。要開始建立提醒，請先搜尋任何物品，然後點擊左側的「提醒」分頁。"

#: pages/about.tsx:49
msgid "All market information is available: Prices, Materia, Retainer, Crafters and even Buyers. Everything that you see in-game is available. Additional data-views have been added such as graphs, extended history and cross-world summary is also included."
msgstr "所有市場交易板資訊都可獲得：價格、魔晶石、雇員、製作者甚至買家。包括您能在遊戲中看到的所有內容。同時也包含了額外的資料檢視，例如價格曲線、歷史的交易量和跨服的摘要。"

#: pages/about.tsx:162
msgid "Also thanks to: Vekien, Miu, Mino and all of our uploaders!"
msgstr "額外致謝：Vekien、Miu、Mino 和所有的上傳者們！"

